Abolished 1894 to become the separate parishes of Aberwheeler 
    Urban and Aberwheeler Rural.

Created 1894 from the rural part of the parish of Aberwheeler. 
    Renamed 1.4.1974 to become the community of Aberwheeler. See also Table 2, note 
    (d).

Created 1894 from the part of the parish of Aberwheeler in Denbigh 
    Municipal Borough. Abolished 1.4.1935 and added to the parish of Denbigh.
See Table 2, notes (a) and (d).

See Table 2, notes (a) and (d).
